      "text": [
        "2221 - وَ مَنْ حَجَّ يُرِيدُ بِهِ وَجْهَ اَللَّهِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ لاَ يُرِيدُ بِهِ رِيَاءً وَ لاَ سُمْعَةً غَفَرَ اَللَّهُ لَهُ اَلْبَتَّةَ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2221 - Whoever performs Hajj seeking the pleasure of Allah (swt), Mighty and Majestic, without intending to show off or gain reputation, Allah (swt) will forgive them completely."
        ]
      }
    },
